727453f-a.title: Queens: Myrtle Avenue - Union Turnpike
727453f-a.text:
Myrtle Ave., north side, between Union Turnpike and 81st Road, showing a roadhouse belonging to Weln and 2erweck, the brewer. These
buiidings were demolished prior to 1929.
May 1923.
Eumene L. Armbruster Collection.
